SUMMARY:Houston Linux User Group
DTSTAMP:20260618T044223Z
DTSTART:20260618T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Are you interested or already invested in the Linux Operating S
	ystem?\nJoin us at the Houston Linux User Group\, one of the oldest user g
	roups involved with the Linux Operating System. We discuss new trends in o
	perating system usage\, software development\, and current technological t
	rends\, as well as provide one-on-one training or class-based instruction.
	 Learn about how to get more out of your computer or how to leverage any o
	f the Linux-based computational platforms.\nAll are welcome to attend\, re
	gardless of whether you’re a seasoned Linux professional intent on network
	ing or a new Linux user struggling with installation or the command line.\
	nThis monthly meeting includes all of the standard Houston Linux User Grou
	p meeting activities\, which include meet-and-greet\, presentations of per
	sonal projects\, multi-meeting classes\, as well as organizational and coo
	rdinating announcements. \nVisit our website at: https://www.houstonlinux.
	org/\nVisit our calendar and the agenda of each week’s meeting at: https:/
	/calendar.google.com/calendar/u/0/embed?src=houstonlinuxusergroup@gmail.co
	m \nJoin us on social media.\nDiscord: https://discord.gg/MPzYfeJz\nReddit
	: https://www.reddit.com/r/houstonlinuxusergroup/\n\nhttps://iondistrict.c
	om/event/houston-linux-user-group-5/\n\nFrom Ion District
URL:https://iondistrict.com/event/houston-linux-user-group-5/
LOCATION:Ion – Conference Room 029 – 030\, 4201 Main St\, Houston\, TX\, 77
	002\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:ion-district
CATEGORIES:Ion District
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
